  "title": "Senior Manager, Change Management",
  "description": "<p>We are partnering with a leading telecom client to hire a Change Manager (Technology & Transformation) to drive organisation-wide change, especially across technology-led transformation initiatives.<br /></p><p>Responsibilities:</p><ul><li>Lead change management for major technology and transformation projects.</li><li>Plan and deliver stakeholder engagement, readiness, impact assessments, communications, and training.</li><li>Partner with technology vendors and internal teams to define roles, outcomes, and success measures.</li><li>Build and maintain a change management playbook with tools, templates, and best practices.</li><li>Coach and enable stakeholders to apply change management at scale.</li><li>Promote change management as a core organisational capability.</li><li>Stakeholders: HR, business leaders, internal teams and external technology partners<br /></li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>10+ years’ experience in change management, including 4+ years as a Change Manager.</li><li>Proven success in multi-location or multi-country technology adoption projects.</li><li>Change management certification (e.g. Prosci) preferred.</li><li>Strong stakeholder management and communication skills.</li><li>Experience building scalable change processes and tools.</li></ul>",
